  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the diced onion and sauté until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute until fragrant.",
    "Add the ground coriander, ground cumin, and tomato paste; cook for another 2 minutes.",
    "Pour in the diced tomatoes and vegetable broth, bring to a gentle simmer.",
    "Add the drained chickpeas, reduce heat to low, and simmer for 20 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Whisk the yogurt until smooth, then stir it into the stew along with the lemon juice; heat until thickened but not boiling.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste, garnish with optional parsley, and serve hot."
  ],
